%N A395781 Expansion of (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(4*k+1,k) * x^k)^3.
%F A395781 a(n) = Sum_{i,j,k >= 0 and i+j+k=n} binomial(4*i+1,i) * binomial(4*j+1,j) * binomial(4*k+1,k).
%F A395781 G.f.: B(x)^3 where B(x) is the g.f. of A052203.
%F A395781 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} (k+1) * 3^k * binomial(4*n+5,n-k).
%F A395781 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} (k+1) * 4^k * binomial(4*n+3-k,n-k).
%F A395781 a(0) = 1; a(n) = (1/n) * Sum_{k=0..n-1} (4*k+15) * 3^k * binomial(k+2,2) * binomial(4*n+5,n-1-k).
%F A395781 a(0) = 1; a(n) = (1/n) * Sum_{k=0..n-1} (3*k+15) * 4^k * binomial(k+2,2) * binomial(4*n+2-k,n-1-k).
%o A395781 (PARI) a(n) = sum(k=0, n, (k+1)*3^k*binomial(4*n+5, n-k));
%Y A395781 Cf. A052203, A308523, A395782.
